android.os.Parcelable, com.microblink.blinkinput.intent.MBIntentTransferable
public final class FieldByFieldBundle extends com.microblink.blinkinput.intent.BaseIntentTransferable<FieldByFieldBundle>
Represents a bundle of FieldByFieldElement objects that can travel via Intent. Used inside FieldByFieldUISettings which is used by FieldByFieldOverlayController and FieldByFieldScanActivity.
